props.ABBR_TITLE: object: Target designation (as given by the astronomer)
dp_tech: Mode/technique used for the observation

tpl_id: The observing template identifier, a unique ID assigned to a template, that is, to a pre-defined sequence of operations involving any combination of telescope, instrument and detector actions.
tpl_start: The start time of the execution of the observing template.
exptime: Total exposure time on target
mjd_obs: Modified Julian Date (JD - 2400000.5) of the start of the observation
tel_airm_start: The airmass at the start of the observation
